            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Z. N. <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_55171" ref="#person_19827"><forename>Julius</forename></rs> und <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_55172" ref="#person_19823"><forename>Helene</forename></rs> bei uns.―</p>
